				<title>星巴克 AI库存系统仅上线9个月即被放弃：咖啡连锁数字化转型到底卡在哪？</title>
				<link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/xing-ba-ke-aiku-cun-xi-tong-jin-shang-xian-9ge-yue/</link>
